title: BR-Mosque1.3.rar
description: This is a new release of BR-Mosque, a large indoor/outdoor Bombing Run map for UT2004. The setting is a holy site between the desert and the sea, with some spectacular Z-axis play. This is a very large map, suitable for 32 players. The new version includes both bug fixes and enhancements, including some tweeks of the Bot AI to improve ball passing. See the bundled file v1.3Changes.rtf for details of all the fixes and improvements. This new version also includes an equivalent CTF map.
